window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>My older brother is dead. And my trials have already begun.</b></p> <p>After saving Hamelin and earning the loyalty of Princess Adriana, I’m called back to Sevona to claim my birthright as crown prince.</p> <p>But the road home is anything but simple. A hidden dwarf city is under siege. A relentless knight in black armor watches my every move. And a rival noble house schemes to tear our kingdom apart for another’s favor.</p> <p>With my girls beside me and new allies joining the fight, I’ll need every ounce of strength and cunning to earn my crown.</p> <p>I was born to rule. Now, I’ll prove it.</p>"; 
